The paper involves using a convolutional neural network to match audio streams to sheet music images, which suggests that it could fall under the categories of computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the use of neural networks and machine learning techniques could place it under the sub-categories of signal processing (cs.SI) and sound (cs.SD).
